    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Can vim._ui_flush() be replaced with vim.api.nvim__redraw({flush=True}) or similar?\r\n\r\nThe existing `flush` would update pending window updates, which I think is unwanted here. `nvim__redraw` intentionally didn't expose `ui_flush()`. Could still be added as `ui_flush` or something if there is a need for it. IDK if that is preferred over what you have here.",
